* create a folder hadoop and sub folder bin of hadoop in spark-3.0.1-bin-hadoop2.7 folder 

* visit to the link https://github.com/steveloughran/winutils and download winutils 
 Past downloaded winutils file into folder spark-3.0.1-bin-hadoop2.7\hadoop\bin
 
 * open command prompt and change the current directory to 
cd D:\bigdata_lab\spark-3.0.1-bin-hadoop2.7\bin 
 set HADOOP_HOME=D:\bigdata_lab\spark-3.0.1-bin-hadoop2.7\hadoop\bin 

* inside spark bin folder run spark as spark-shell

